Run pure sequential:

./scripts/run_test.sh BS

output file: sequential_bsBS.out

Run distributed:

NP=1..max nodes

Caution: srun does not work well in altec
srun -N NP -n NP --exclusive ./scripts/run_test_distr.sh NP BS

sbatch -N NP --exclusive ./scripts/run_test_distr.sh NP BS

output file: distr_nNP_bsBS.out

